Authors of CGIpaf

Staf Wagemakers, Main author.

Andreas Liebe, fixed some bugs 

 * created a patch which allows it to use mailcfg.cgi for users with 
   non-interactive shell such as /bin/false
 * fixed a accessdb bug, the database wasn't always closed.

Daniel R.,

 * created a patch with the ability to list words in /etc/cgipaf.conf that 
   should not be a part of new passwords.

Fabricio Machado
  * Brazilian Portuguese translation

Koen de Jonge
  * Dutch translation


